videos.description: Colorado State's Emmanuel Omogbo gets free on the break and crushes the one-handed dunk without paying any attention to the San Diego State defender he puts on a poster.
videos.headline: Omogbo crushes the rim with vicious dunk

videos.description: San Diego State's Winston Shepard puts on the sweet spin move down low to get through three Colorado State defenders and then throws down the vicious two-hand dunk and appropriate scream.
videos.headline: Spin move through the defense for huge dunk? Yes please!
